v1.4.0: affiliate program, social links, paid-plan payment gating

- Affiliate & referrals screen: shareable link, referral list, earnings;
  earn 10% to your wallet when a referral buys a paid plan.
- Social profile links (LinkedIn/GitHub/Twitter/Instagram/Website) in the
  profile editor for both roles.
- Paid plans no longer activate by clicking — tapping Upgrade routes to an
  online payment (server returns 402 until payments are enabled); only Free
  switches instantly.

Adds AffiliateResponse models + GET /api/affiliate + WalletRepository.affiliate,
Screen.Affiliate + AffiliateScreen, Account row, and social fields on the
profile request/response models.

